This one is also known as S01E17
Chairman of the Hoard
March 30, 2011

Just to make it clear - this is NOT the real S02E05, it is a mislabeled by sHoTV release of S01E17 "Chairman of the Hoard" (much earlier episode). I cannot rename the torrent because the TPB Edit torrent feature is broken for months.

There seems to be no real S02E05 on TPB at this moment.
